"{\"uid\": \"citizen.co.za-sport-semenya-defence-intersex-boxers-paris-olympics\", \"noun_phrases\": [{\"sentence\": \"Home\\u00bbSport ByWesley Botton Chief sports journalist 3 minute read 6 August 2024 01:40 pm Caster Semenya during a hearing at the European Court of Human Rights earlier this year.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 182, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 21, \"end\": 27, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Botton,_North_Yorkshire\", \"score\": 0.901131173431149, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Botton\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Botton,_North_Yorkshire\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Botton,_North_Yorkshire\"}, {\"begin\": 94, \"end\": 108, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Caster_Semenya\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Caster Semenya\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Caster_Semenya\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Caster_Semenya\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"3 minute\", \"from\": 51, \"to\": 59}, {\"ngram\": \"a hearing\", \"from\": 110, \"to\": 119}, {\"ngram\": \"the European Court\", \"from\": 123, \"to\": 141}, {\"ngram\": \"Human Rights\", \"from\": 145, \"to\": 157}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Picture: Frederick Florin/AFP Two-time Olympic 800m champion Caster Semenya has called on international sporting authorities to standardise gender rules and protect intersex athletes from discrimination.\", \"from\": 183, \"to\": 387, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 192, \"end\": 201, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Frederick_the_Great\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.655650942865743e-17, \"text\": \"Frederick\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Frederick_the_Great\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Frederick_the_Great\"}, {\"begin\": 209, \"end\": 212, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Agence_France-Presse\", \"score\": 0.9999999047597657, \"rank\": 9.52396545057344e-08, \"text\": \"AFP\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Agence_France-Presse\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Agence_France-Presse\"}, {\"begin\": 245, \"end\": 259, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Caster_Semenya\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Caster Semenya\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Caster_Semenya\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Caster_Semenya\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Picture\", \"from\": 183, \"to\": 190}, {\"ngram\": \"international sporting authorities\", \"from\": 273, \"to\": 307}, {\"ngram\": \"gender rules\", \"from\": 323, \"to\": 335}, {\"ngram\": \"intersex athletes\", \"from\": 348, \"to\": 365}, {\"ngram\": \"discrimination\", \"from\": 371, \"to\": 385}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Semenya was banned from competing against women last year by World Athletics, along with other track athletes with differences of sexual development (DSD), a decision the South African star is still fighting in court.\", \"from\": 389, \"to\": 606, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 450, \"end\": 465, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Athletics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.1415566795984682e-16, \"text\": \"World Athletics\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Athletics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Athletics\"}, {\"begin\": 539, \"end\": 542, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Signals_Directorate\", \"score\": 0.99994015504852, \"rank\": 5.984853317867407e-05, \"text\": \"DSD\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q327333\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Signals_Directorate\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Signals_Directorate\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Semenya\", \"from\": 389, \"to\": 396}, {\"ngram\": \"women\", \"from\": 431, \"to\": 436}, {\"ngram\": \"other track athletes\", \"from\": 478, \"to\": 498}, {\"ngram\": \"differences\", \"from\": 504, \"to\": 515}, {\"ngram\": \"sexual development\", \"from\": 519, \"to\": 537}, {\"ngram\": \"a decision\", \"from\": 545, \"to\": 555}, {\"ngram\": \"the South African star\", \"from\": 556, \"to\": 578}, {\"ngram\": \"court\", \"from\": 600, \"to\": 605}]}, {\"sentence\": \"ALSO READ:Semenya hopes latest hearing will protect dignity of athletes In some sports, however, DSD athletes are still able to compete, with Algeria's Imane Khelif and Taiwan's Lin Yu-ting receiving widespread criticism during the ongoingOlympic Gamesin Paris, where both athletes secured medals.\", \"from\": 608, \"to\": 906, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 706, \"end\": 709, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Signals_Directorate\", \"score\": 0.99994015504852, \"rank\": 5.984853317867407e-05, \"text\": \"DSD\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q327333\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Signals_Directorate\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Signals_Directorate\"}, {\"begin\": 751, \"end\": 758, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\", \"score\": 0.9999921597850908, \"rank\": 7.148103230593115e-06, \"text\": \"Algeria\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\"}, {\"begin\": 778, \"end\": 784, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taiwan\", \"score\": 0.9999230155775428, \"rank\": 7.289104153992889e-05, \"text\": \"Taiwan\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taiwan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taiwan\"}, {\"begin\": 787, \"end\": 798, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lin_Yu-ting\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Lin Yu-ting\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lin_Yu-ting\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lin_Yu-ting\"}, {\"begin\": 864, \"end\": 869, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999980048343681, \"rank\": 1.9951695517183887e-06, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Semenya\", \"from\": 618, \"to\": 625}, {\"ngram\": \"latest hearing\", \"from\": 632, \"to\": 646}, {\"ngram\": \"dignity\", \"from\": 660, \"to\": 667}, {\"ngram\": \"athletes\", \"from\": 671, \"to\": 679}, {\"ngram\": \"some sports\", \"from\": 683, \"to\": 694}, {\"ngram\": \"widespread criticism\", \"from\": 808, \"to\": 828}, {\"ngram\": \"secured medals\", \"from\": 890, \"to\": 904}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Though both boxers had been prevented from competing at the World Championships last year, after tests revealed they had unusually high testosterone levels, that event was organised by theInternational Boxing Association(IBA) which is no longer recognised by the International Olympic Committee (IOC).\", \"from\": 908, \"to\": 1209, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1171, \"end\": 1202, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"International Olympic Committee\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"both boxers\", \"from\": 915, \"to\": 926}, {\"ngram\": \"the World Championships\", \"from\": 964, \"to\": 987}, {\"ngram\": \"tests\", \"from\": 1005, \"to\": 1010}, {\"ngram\": \"unusually high testosterone levels\", \"from\": 1029, \"to\": 1063}, {\"ngram\": \"that event\", \"from\": 1065, \"to\": 1075}, {\"ngram\": \"theInternational Boxing Association(IBA\", \"from\": 1093, \"to\": 1132}, {\"ngram\": \"IOC\", \"from\": 1204, \"to\": 1207}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The IOC organised the boxing tournament at theParis Games, clearing Khelif and Yu-ting to participate.\", \"from\": 1211, \"to\": 1313, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1215, \"end\": 1218, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.212831934175075e-27, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the boxing tournament\", \"from\": 1229, \"to\": 1250}, {\"ngram\": \"theParis Games\", \"from\": 1254, \"to\": 1268}, {\"ngram\": \"Khelif\", \"from\": 1279, \"to\": 1285}, {\"ngram\": \"Yu-ting\", \"from\": 1290, \"to\": 1297}]}, {\"sentence\": \"While she had retired from competitive running, Semenya felt it was important that gender rules affecting DSD athletes were consistent across the various sports.\", \"from\": 1315, \"to\": 1476, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1421, \"end\": 1424, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Signals_Directorate\", \"score\": 0.99994015504852, \"rank\": 5.984853317867407e-05, \"text\": \"DSD\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q327333\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Signals_Directorate\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Signals_Directorate\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"competitive running\", \"from\": 1342, \"to\": 1361}, {\"ngram\": \"Semenya\", \"from\": 1363, \"to\": 1370}, {\"ngram\": \"gender rules\", \"from\": 1398, \"to\": 1410}, {\"ngram\": \"the various sports\", \"from\": 1457, \"to\": 1475}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"What happened at the Olympics now is not what happened in my space.\", \"from\": 1478, \"to\": 1546, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 1496, \"to\": 1508}, {\"ngram\": \"my space\", \"from\": 1537, \"to\": 1545}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Each organisation has its own policy.\", \"from\": 1547, \"to\": 1584, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Each organisation\", \"from\": 1547, \"to\": 1564}, {\"ngram\": \"its own policy\", \"from\": 1569, \"to\": 1583}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Boxing has its own and athletics has its own,\\\" Semenya said in an interview withSportsBoom.\", \"from\": 1585, \"to\": 1676, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Boxing\", \"from\": 1585, \"to\": 1591}, {\"ngram\": \"athletics\", \"from\": 1608, \"to\": 1617}, {\"ngram\": \"Semenya\", \"from\": 1632, \"to\": 1639}, {\"ngram\": \"an interview withSportsBoom\", \"from\": 1648, \"to\": 1675}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's not about what I want, but about principles of life.\", \"from\": 1678, \"to\": 1736, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"principles\", \"from\": 1717, \"to\": 1727}, {\"ngram\": \"life\", \"from\": 1731, \"to\": 1735}]}, {\"sentence\": \"My views are not about me because I have ventured more into coaching now.\\\"\", \"from\": 1737, \"to\": 1811, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"My views\", \"from\": 1737, \"to\": 1745}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Semenya defended Algerian fighter Khelif, who had taken the brunt of criticism on social media, with many people incorrectly claiming she was transgender and calling for sporting authorities to ensure women were protected, particularly in contact sports.\", \"from\": 1813, \"to\": 2067, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1830, \"end\": 1838, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\", \"score\": 0.9820219849172446, \"rank\": 0.018235032417059933, \"text\": \"Algerian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Semenya\", \"from\": 1813, \"to\": 1820}, {\"ngram\": \"the brunt\", \"from\": 1869, \"to\": 1878}, {\"ngram\": \"criticism\", \"from\": 1882, \"to\": 1891}, {\"ngram\": \"social media\", \"from\": 1895, \"to\": 1907}, {\"ngram\": \"many people\", \"from\": 1914, \"to\": 1925}, {\"ngram\": \"sporting authorities\", \"from\": 1983, \"to\": 2003}, {\"ngram\": \"women\", \"from\": 2014, \"to\": 2019}, {\"ngram\": \"contact sports\", \"from\": 2052, \"to\": 2066}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Imane is a great boxer and people always criticise when someone is doing well,\\\" Semenya said.\", \"from\": 2069, \"to\": 2163, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Imane\", \"from\": 2070, \"to\": 2075}, {\"ngram\": \"a great boxer\", \"from\": 2079, \"to\": 2092}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 2097, \"to\": 2103}, {\"ngram\": \"someone\", \"from\": 2126, \"to\": 2133}, {\"ngram\": \"Semenya\", \"from\": 2150, \"to\": 2157}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"People will always talk then.\", \"from\": 2165, \"to\": 2195, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"People\", \"from\": 2166, \"to\": 2172}]}, {\"sentence\": \"When she wasn't winning, then everyone was quiet.\\\"\", \"from\": 2196, \"to\": 2246, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"everyone\", \"from\": 2226, \"to\": 2234}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This is so Painful to watch.\", \"from\": 2248, \"to\": 2276, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I have been boxing for years in the International Boxing Association which has committed INJUSTICE towards me.~#Imane_Khelifpic.twitter.com/NH7GeM9YoK The debate around intersex athletes was far from over, but Semenya called on the IOC to protect them against discrimination.\", \"from\": 2276, \"to\": 2553, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2313, \"end\": 2345, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Women's_International_Boxing_Association\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.222205998613411e-19, \"text\": \"International Boxing Association\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Women's_International_Boxing_Association\", \"dbpedia\": \"htt